RE:  Possess THC with intent to deliver as repeater on 04-29-14.

Defendant in custody.  The State informs the Court that the defendant will be charged with the crime of possess THC with intent to deliver as repeater.  The matter is continued for initial appearance on 05-19-14 at 2:30 p.m. Bail is set at $8,000.00 recognizance bond with the conditions that he have no contact with any known drug users or sellers, that he report to the Manitowoc County Sheriff's Department daily, by 4:00 p.m. and that he not consume any controlled substance without a prescription.  Bail furnished and defendant is released from custody.
